{"tid":1946672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那湖北江西公安互揪笑下好喇，唔好真係咁傻信支那人會反共","createTime":"2020-03-27T18:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T23:38:10.000Z","uid":36775,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b0521ec9532ea06a2f8558125586f39882e3361b","tid":1946672,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:49:40.000Z","msg":"六四當日成個支那巨震，支那人個個話支持學生<br />\n過咗30年支那人可以掉翻轉幫共產黨洗白六四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n李文亮死頭幾日日日話要言論自由<br />\n將責任推去派出所就扮盲乜都睇唔到<br />\n就連文化大革命死幾千萬人嘅人禍都可以扮唔知<br />\n提就話要向前看，連用口屌政府都唔敢<br />\n證明支那人就係一個垃圾人種<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好咁傻仔信支那人會真係反共<br />\n支那人種奴性帝王基因植根三千年<br />\n即使香港有英國人管都洗唔走<br />\n更加唔好expect支那人會好過香港人<br />\n對一個用口屌政府都唔敢嘅民族去反共?<br />\n仲難撚過登陸太陽<br />\n<br />\n只要維尼同支共搵江西公安局一個局長祭旗<br />\n再加話訓誡下個公安局<br />\n話支那人要團結對抗疫情<br />\n加上平時微博洗版笑下美國歐洲咁多人有支那武漢肺炎<br />\n各國封城係抄支那做法，支那幫全世界<br />\n搞所謂民族自豪感<br />\n同引發支那人來自對白人自卑而來嘅虛榮感<br />\n支那人的智商係唔會發覺自己報假數，篤少幾十萬<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最尾咪又係個個拍手讚維尼，政府好野</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信可以靠支那人種突然覺醒去反共?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那人就係賤，對支那人有期望就係on9 </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4da84e93f7dd300ad4a98eb169f2276eed0a746f","tid":1946672,"uid":36775,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:50:14.000Z","msg":"信支那人天真過天真嬌"},{"pid":"d125671ae108779c93d9b2fd17fd9fa7889a03b6","tid":1946672,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952073ac12daa199e35ebf7f64a205170ad9efa0","tid":1946672,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:51:47.000Z","msg":"未到比美帝打果刻，支那仔都唔會反共啦<br />\n支那狗只係free rider"},{"pid":"50168ae12e4d33126e8a215a396da1901e29825f","tid":1946672,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:53:08.000Z","msg":"警世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ffd83e8b42262e516048a5294d3c07ac1ae405","tid":1946672,"uid":106736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"朝三暮四不嬲都係支那人特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9eb7db6e60c681f800ea64afdaed5605fb3f8b","tid":1946672,"uid":36775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"952073ac12daa199e35ebf7f64a205170ad9efa0","tid":1946672,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:51:47.000Z","msg":"未到比美帝打果刻，支那仔都唔會反共啦<br />\n支那狗只係free rider"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:55:00.000Z","msg":"要改變對支那人有期望嘅思想<br />\n消除內心有大中華膠基因"},{"pid":"4b02407af1f7cd461fa70716388f99784b7f2ee1","tid":1946672,"uid":15605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:55:05.000Z","msg":"互揪唔好笑，死曬先好笑"},{"pid":"d7421b9b7f9f7c067926172a036e12d3849e10b7","tid":1946672,"uid":136900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:55:12.000Z","msg":"今次都起碼有1000萬人消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5fa63a8a7fab4ae92ff5881d744eea758ef2fd","tid":1946672,"uid":105522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T19:03:37.000Z","msg":"唔係期望佢哋覺醒 但支那亂支共要出多啲力維穩 唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b196da278a925787e3db1cc97af26d755161fa7","tid":1946672,"uid":163149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T19:05:03.000Z","msg":"點解要信佢覺醒<br />\n支那人只會為自己利益<br /